        <div id="how-prog-teach">
            <h3>How do Programmers Help Each Other Improve?</h3>
            <p>
                The programming community uses a variety of means to help each other improve.
            </p>
            <p>
                One common method is tutorials, like the ones Derek Banas produce. For example: <br/>
