                <br/>
                This tutorial is targeted at beginners. This is seen by Derek not assuming knowledge as well as the calm tone and the slower pace of this video.
            </p>
            <p>
                Another common method of helping other programmers is through blog posts such as <a href="http://blogs.tedneward.com/post/the-vietnam-of-computer-science/">this one</a> 
